bug.short_desc: Target measure of measure filter is changed when reopen the filter dialog[1102]

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 86134 report design
Description: Target measure of measure filter is changed when reopen the filter dialog[1102]
Build number: 2.3.0.v20080104-0800
Steps to reproduce: 1, New a crosstab at least two measures 2, New a Measure filter and select the second measure in Measure list 3, Specify all the required fields and click OK 4, Reopen the filter dialog
Expected result: The Measure is as former specified
Actual result: The Measure is changed the first one in the list
It seems that the combo isn't initialized. Will fix it soon.
Verified in v20080128-0800 build, close the bug.
